title: How [Not] to Kiss a Prince
description: Let the Magical Mayhem begin! Cindy Eller has not one, but two weddings to prepare for in less than two weeks when the cupcakes hit the fan-- a mysterious man has appeared claiming to be betrothed to Cindy and insisting she must marry him before her sister's nuptials can take place.Obviously this doesn't sit well with Cindy's Ordinary boyfriend.That's the way the cake-- and the wedding-- crumbles!
author: Elizabeth A. Reeves
